snippet.title: SICKO SANCTUM 2 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Enemies are weapons.
Style is power.
Your only goal, total violence. 

SICKO SANCTUM 2 is an innovative score-attack movement-shooter crafted from the design lessons of modern classics such as ULTRAKILL and HYPER DEMON. Featuring a simple player move-set in combination with synergistic enemy design, SICKO SANCTUM 2 represents the cutting-edge of digitized violence. 

WISHLIST ON STEAM NOW
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3332660/SICKO_SANCTUM_2/

In game and trailer music by WaywardWisp, check out their SoundCloud!
https://soundcloud.com/WaywardWisp
